com.sap.cloud.sdk.datamodel.odata.helper

Interface OneToOneLink<EntityT,LinkedEntityT>

  • Type Parameters:
    EntityT - The entity where the link starts.
    LinkedEntityT - The entity where the link ends (i.e. the related entity).

    public interface OneToOneLink<EntityT,LinkedEntityT>
    Interface designed to be implemented by EntityLink class in order to provide a filter function.
